Description: branding assets for Aptura OS
 Installs Aptura OS wallpapers, logo assets, GTK fallback theme, icon theme,
 COSMIC color palettes, Plymouth theme, GRUB menu defaults, and derivative
 metadata used by live-build hooks and desktop integration.
